==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: life-of-man
<hw>life-of-man</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>An unarmed woody rhizomatous
perennial plant (<spn>Aralia racemosa</spn>) distinguished from wild
sarsaparilla by more aromatic roots and panicled umbels; it grows from
Southeastern North America to Mexico.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> American spikenard, petty morel, <spn>Aralia
racemosa</spn>.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Life-preserver</ent>⟦br⟧
